org.jpws.pwslib.data
Class RawFieldList

java.lang.Object
  org.jpws.pwslib.data.RawFieldList
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
HeaderFieldList
public class RawFieldList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable

RawFieldList implements a map from field names (0..255) into type PwsRawField. As field names function the "field types" as the assumption on each rawfield list is that any field type may occur only once.

Fields returned by this list are a deep clone of the listed fields.

Since:
2-0-0
